Plot: two people from completely different worlds meet by chance, thrown together as if by fate. their attraction is immediately obvious and overwhelming. he is attracted to her beauty (she is a supermodel) and good humor; she is seduced by his charisma and honesty. with his gifts of poetry and tenderness, he opens her heart to the possibility of true love. but it takes a lot of courage to make a commitment. is she truly in love with him? and even if she is, will she able to leave the cosmopolitan, superficial lifestyle to be with him?
Title: fall
